"--------------
" Key mapping
"--------------
" Disable arrow keys
noremap <UP> <NOP>
noremap <DOWN> <NOP>
noremap <LEFT> <NOP>
noremap <RIGHT> <NOP>
inoremap <UP> <NOP>
inoremap <DOWN> <NOP>
inoremap <LEFT> <NOP>
inoremap <RIGHT> <NOP>

" Map `Shift+n` to toggle NERDTree
nnoremap <silent> <S-n> :NERDTreeToggle<CR>
